Package com.adobe.pdfservices.operation.pdfjobs.result

package com.adobe.pdfservices.operation.pdfjobs.result
Contains the result classes and sub-packages for PDFServicesJob implementations in the com.adobe.pdfservices.operation.pdfjobs.jobs package.
